017package org.microbean.type;
018
019import java.lang.reflect.WildcardType;
020
021/**
022 * A {@link java.lang.reflect.WildcardType} implementation that has no
023 * bounds, i.e. has only a single {@linkplain
024 * java.lang.reflect.WildcardType#getUpperBounds() upper bound} of
025 * {@link Object Object.class}.
026 *
027 * @author <a href="https://about.me/lairdnelson"
028 * target="_parent">Laird Nelson</a>
029 *
030 * @see java.lang.reflect.WildcardType
031 *
032 * @see java.lang.reflect.WildcardType#getUpperBounds()
033 */
034public final class UnboundedWildcardType extends AbstractWildcardType {
035
036  /**
037   * The sole instance of this class.
038   */
039  public static final WildcardType INSTANCE = new UnboundedWildcardType();
040  
041  private UnboundedWildcardType() {
042    super(null, null);
043  }
044
045}
